NUMBER 1856
REGION 2
NAME Instadtoo's hearth
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
DEEPCAVE
CHANNEL 82
LIMITED_MOVEMENT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Woven strands of kelp stuffed with dried fungus provide Instadtoo with a comfortable place to sit and meditate. The walls of the room are painted with curious little stick figures that depict the daily routine of the gurk.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 1854
ITEM 0 1338
IFVERB GAZE -1
	ECHO PLAYER Staring at Instadtoo will not get you anywhere, try listening.
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
	SKILLCHECK 32 -40 DUMMY1
	IFVAR DUMMY1 < 0
		ECHO PLAYER You are unable to discover the key to understanding Instadtoo's mumbling.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR DUMMY1 >= 0
		ECHO PLAYER You realize that despite her age and frailty, Instadtoo knows quite a bit. The secret to finding out what she has to say is to ask one word and two word questions like "who?" "how?" Deep Realms?" and the like.
		EQUAL INTNUM23 1
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY HELLO?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Hello."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo does not seem to understand your language. Perhaps if you listen to her carefully, you will be able to learn how to communicate with her.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY WHO?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "We are the gurk, we come from the surface world, but we have been here a very long time."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY HOW?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "You must get the favor of Chartuukow, he is a bit greedy for trinkets. He can feel the remnants of magic in them, and it makes him happy. Give him a good deal on something. Also he will cast the spell 'Water
Equilibrium' on you, and you will be able to breath in water. From then on, you will be able to live in water, until the next time you take a breath of air in this cavern."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY WHERE?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Legends say our planet crashed into this one, somewhere near on the surface, but the light and temperatures were too harsh up there, so we came below."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY WHEN?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "We were happy here since time out of mind, we used to mine elkyri fir the sharkhor but they got greedy and enslaved us. We were at war with them for many years. We lost very badly. Only I Moiya, and Chartuuko
w, the old ones, are left. Soon our hatchlings will grow, and we shall mount a war against Culumra. We hope that now you have found your way here, you will aid us."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY WHY?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Culumra want to rule the world. His servants the sharkhor even now plot to slay all air breathers."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY DEEP_REALMS?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "This is the end of the Deep Realms. Before us are the Deeplanders, the Fungal Jungle and the lair of Ming Ktuk. Next you may return to your world by the river, or have Chartuukow help you breath under water,
so that you may slay the sharkhor in their domain."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY PEARLS?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "I could never reveal the source of our pearls!."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo glares at you.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY GURKAN_PEARLS?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "I could never reveal the source of our pearls!."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo glares at you.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY TALISMAN?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "The bone talisman Moiya wears contains the power to keep the old ones from dying while the hatchlings are growing."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY MOIYA?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Moiya is our shaman and healer. You may ask her 'heal?'"
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY CHARTUUKOW?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Chartuukow is our mate, he makes the eggs grow. He dabbles in magic a bit. If you ask him for help, he will."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY sharkhor?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Vile creatures! I beg you to slay them as you see them. The sharkhor are an ancient race, neither shark, nor humanoid -- but both. They are enthralled to their god-king Calumra, who they serve unquestioningl
y."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY CALUMRA?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Calumra, god-king of the sharkhor, is a gargantuan octopus of unknown origin and indeterminate age. It is unquestionably the lord of the deep sea, but it is whispered that it is jealous of the of the air-bre
hers who walk the surface, and seeks to extend its rule over them as well. He must be stopped!"
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY WAR?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Culumra sends his sharkhor to the surface to steal the breath of air breathers. It is said that when he has accumulated enough breath, he can rule the world. The sharkhor would like that."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY FUTURE?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "With the threat of Culumra muted, Andor will live to have a renaissance of the arts and the mind."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY PRESENT?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "This is the now, all that you see tempered by what you have seen."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY PAST?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "The past is gone, do not long for it."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY DEEPLANDERS?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "They are cousins of the highlanders that were driven deeper into the depths of Andor during the early years following the Cataclysm. They are an industrious group, but unlike we gurk, their culture has suffer
ed due to isolation. The are a bit crude."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY TARINTH?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "I don't know who that is."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY SYRIX?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "He's a fool."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY MALTHESIA?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO ALL Instadtoo cringes.
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Ware!  Do not attract the gaze of the dark one by speaking his name."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY ENDIR?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "He's one of the great blue haired lovers of all time."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY MING_KTUK?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
                ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Ming Ktuk was a benefactor of ours. I believe you would call him a dragon. He passed this way once as he went to his lair. We had much gold clutter at the time, and he seemed to want it so we ga
ve it to him. He offered us power or wisdom. I chose wisdom. He gave us the power to make the light globes with which we grow \
our food. He also taught us how to imprison our enemies. Would that we were strong enough to travel to Culumra. We could wreak havoc someday, when our hatchlings are ready."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY MURG?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "There once were an enclave of murg in the Deep Realms, they served Ming Ktuk. But even the mightiest of magic can not keep nature from running her course. The eventually died of old age. I do not know who ser
s Ming Ktuk now."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY gorgalask?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
                ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "It is a hideous reptilian creature known for its ferocity, massive jaws and poisonous bite. It is said that meeting the gorgalask's gaze is death. Fortunately, there are very few that reach th
e adult stage. Certain of its body parts are known to contain powerful chemical properties."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY lurker?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "A menace to peaceful cave-dwellers, the lurker is stupid yet cunning. Watch your back in any place where they are known to live."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY haunt?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Sad... There are some evil forces that thrive here that I do not wish to ponder."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY sekleth?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "A brutal and incredibly stupid forerunner of the drakin. They are constantly hungry and will battle anything that looks like food."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY fungus?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Fungus takes many forms, some of it benign, some malevolent. Some of it is useful as food, while other fungus can have magical properties. Some hostil fungae will take over the bodies of living creatures and
ontinue to use their housing even after death. Parts of these contain excellent properties for use in magic formulations."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY diaman?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "The diamen are a crystalline race that feed upon rocks. They do not bother anyone beyond their own domain, but they are known to be unwelcoming of outsiders. They worship a powerful creature known as the Ka
rghest."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Kharghest?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "A strange and powerful creature, the Kharghest is much like a living cave. It is completely mindless, and its appetite for minerals is insatiable. Many different cave-dwellers have worshiped it through the
ons as some sort of god. It is currently served by the diamen."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY stalactac?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "A peaceful and intelligent race of crystal-eaters, they abhor violence."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Kragenholm?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "A village of deeplanders in the upper caves."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Andor?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Our planet is vast and wonderful, but it is also shrouded in darkness."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Cataclysm?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "It is unknown how much time has passed since the Cataclysm, but it has been at least 1200 years. Probably more. It is testimony to the price of technology."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Technology?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "It shattered our world in the Cataclysm. It was a time of destruction, yet we owe all that we are now to it."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Dahkahn?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO ALL Instadtoo shivers.
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Defiler!  Do you wish to gain notice of the Lord of the Grave?"
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Shemri?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "The earth-mother. She is responsible for the cycles of life and death. She is the most loved god, as most species enjoy breeding so much."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Rorin?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "The god of fire, sun and war. He is not a good god for the gurkan."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Kesken?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "A nice adventuring type, he used to visit and trade with us alot. Used to tell us he was a ranger. I don't know what happened to him. It has been at least one hundered years."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Amilor?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Blessed be the lord of the seas! May he protect and bring you great bounty as you turn back those who would defile his realms."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Kaliban?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "It means "He Who Suffers. But beware, some would take advantage of this one."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Human?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Humans are the elder race of Andor. They were one of the few that remain unchanged since the Cataclysm. The only race that may be older are the dragons."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Dragon?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Dragons are at once native to all worlds and none. They exist in any land that embraces magic, and depart when magic wanes. It is said that they returned to Andor following the Cataclysm."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Aelfen?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "They are a surface race that look like humans, except they are notable for their long lifespans and distinguising pointed ears. I personally think they are vain, primping egoists."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Highlander?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Strong and stalwart mountain and cave dwellers. They are excellent masons and gemcutters. Their women do not have beards you know."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Wolfling?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "I know only that they are a surface race, related somehow to men and wolves."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY DRAKIN?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "An advanced race of reptiles. They are egg layers like us. Were I younger, I would probably like to see what would happen when a male drakin annointed my eggs. What would the offspring be like?"
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Menelian?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "A human of great age and wisdom, and a noteworthy sage of surface creatures. It is said that he has found ways to prolong his life many times beyond the normal span of men. He knows many things... In your
quest for wisdom, you may wish to seek him out. I believe he lives in a hut in the forest of Grymwood."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY GURKAN?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "We are the gurkan, we breath air and water, farm kelp, collect trinkets and live peaceful quiet lives. Except when at war, when we will fight to the death. To do less would be dihororable."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY GURK?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "We are the gurkan, we breath air and water, farm kelp, collect trinkets and live peaceful quiet lives. Except when at war, when we will fight to the death. To do less would be dihororable."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY HELP
	ECHO ALL At the mention of the word "help," Instadtoo opens her eyes for a moment, and gazes out to Chartuukow.
ENDIF
IFSAY PEACE?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Peace? There is no peace in our world, only Paradise, Purgatory and Limbo."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY GOD?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Amilor is our benefactor and diety."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY PURGATORY?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "This is where the black of heart go when they can no longer live, unless of course they become undead."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY PARADISE?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
                ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "It is a wonderful place with pink seas and playful dolphins. I have walked its sands in my dreams. Someday it shall be my home."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY LIMBO?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "This is a place between time. The final maze for those caught between good and evil."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY EVIL?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Evil is insidious, but it has a sense of humor. Much that is evil in the world pretends to be good."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY GOOD?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Good is life and all it cycles, even death. It is the undead aberrations of death that are evil, for they mock both life and death."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY CHAOS?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Some say chaos is the clay from which Andor was formed. I personally think the clay was just clay."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY WISDOM?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "Menelian is the holder of true wisdom."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY MEANING_OF_LIFE?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "A fascinating question, and one I have%cpondered much over the years. Good and evil... Order and chaos. It%cis this and many things, but its purpose eludes me. I know of only
		ECHO PLAYER one other being on Andor with the wisdom and learning of myself, and that is Menelian. Perhaps you can should seek him out."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
		EQUAL INTNUM26 1
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Idemmu_ag?
	IFVAR INTNUM23 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo whispers to you, "A bad place. You should not go there."
		ECHO OTHERS Instadtoo leans toward %n and whispers in %h ear.
		EQUAL INTNUM26 1
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Instadtoo stares at you blankly.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
; The Lair of Ming-K'Tuk and the Focus of Magic
;
VARIABLE DRAGONTAIL
VARIABLE DPASSTAIL
VARIABLE MAKEDRAGON
VARIABLE HANDCOUNT
VARIABLE DRAGDOOROPEN
;
;
MACRO 27
ECHO ALL The doors swing open, followed by a brief burst of warm air.
IFVAR PVAL90 = 0
	ECHO ALL A deep, bellowing voice beckons from beyond:  "Enter, mortals!"
ENDIF
UNLOCK 4
OPEN 4
EQUAL DRAGDOOROPEN TIM
AFFECT 1811
IFVAR MAKEDRAGON = 0
	IFVAR PVAL90 = 0
		GENMON 294
		EQUAL MAKEDRAGON 1
	ELSE
		ROOMCOPY 1813
		NEWITEM 1 232 ADJ1=99
	ENDIF
ENDIF
ECHO ALL You see the heavy elkyri door open.
UNLOCK 4
OPEN 4
AFFECT 1810
CEVENT 44 1 1814
ADD HANDCOUNT 1
CEVENT 49 1 1814
EQUAL READY 0
;
AFFECT 1814
IFVAR HANDCOUNT = 2
	ECHO ALL The silver pentacle begins to glow faintly.
ENDIF
IFVAR HANDCOUNT = 4
	ECHO ALL The silver pentacle glows more intensely.
ENDIF
IFVAR HANDCOUNT = 6
	ECHO ALL The eyes on the statue of the meditating man pop open!
ENDIF
IFVAR HANDCOUNT = 8
	ECHO ALL The hand of the statue opens!
ENDIF
IFVAR HANDCOUNT = 10
	ECHO ALL The hand of the statue closes.
ENDIF
IFVAR HANDCOUNT = 12
	ECHO ALL The eyes of the statue close, and the glow about the pentacle fades.
ENDIF
IFVAR HANDCOUNT > 60
	EQUAL HANDCOUNT 0
ENDIF
;
IFVAR DRAGONTAIL = 1
	IFVAR DPASSTAIL = 1
		EQUAL DRAGONTAIL 0
		EQUAL DPASSTAIL 0
		AFFECT 1811
		ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk places his tail in the way of the eastern passage.
		AFFECT 1812
		ECHO ALL You see Ming-K'Tuk block the western passage with his tail.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
AFFECT 1810
IFITEM 4 OPEN
	IFVAR TIM = 12
		IFVAR DRAGDOOROPEN ! 12
			CLOSE 4
			LOCK 4
			ECHO ALL The huge door slowly swings shut.
			AFFECT 1811
			CLOSE 4
			LOCK 4
			ECHO ALL The huge door slowly swings shut.
			AFFECT 1810			
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	IFVAR TIM = 0
		IFVAR DRAGDOOROPEN ! 0
			CLOSE 4
			LOCK 4
			ECHO ALL The huge door slowly swings shut.
			AFFECT 1811
			CLOSE 4
			LOCK 4
			ECHO ALL The huge door slowly swings shut.
			AFFECT 1811			
		ENDIF
	ENDIF		
ENDIF
;
MACRO 21
IFPREVERB EXAMINE -1
	CLEARVERB
	IFVAR DEAD = 1
		ECHO PLAYER You look upon the shattered form of the Great Wyrm, Ming-K'Tuk. He still looks wondrous, even in death. A sadness touches you as you consider the passing of the dragon.
	ELSE
                ECHO PLAYER Before you, a mountain heaves. The Great Wyrm Ming-K'Tuk is awesome in size and stature, his head alone twice a man's height. Folded up at his back are great, batlike wings of unimagineable length, and his tail coils, almost endlessly, you think, betwixt his mound of gold and jewels. His crimson scales reflect the shaky light with an alien beauty, and his swordlike, ivory claws glisten with razor-sharp precision. You fall on your knees in supplication before this incarnate god.
		POSITION KNEEL
		ECHO OTHERS %N grovels before Ming-K'Tuk.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GIVE -1
	EQUAL DUMMY1 0
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO OTHERS %N presents %a to Ming-K'Tuk.
  	IFVAR INTNUM79 ! 111
    		IFVAR ITEMVAL1 > 10000
      			EQUAL DUMMY1 1
    		ENDIF
    		IFVAR ITEMVAL2 > 5
      			EQUAL DUMMY1 1
    		ENDIF
  		IFVAR ITEMVAL3 >= 100
  			EQUAL DUMMY1 1
    		ENDIF
    		IFVAR DUMMY1 = 0
      			ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "That bauble is of no interest to me!"
    		ELSE
      			ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk snatches %a up in his jaws and flings it into his hoard.
      			ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "Thine tribute is accepted, mortal."
      			REMOVEITEM -1
    			EQUAL FLAG1 0
      			EQUAL INTNUM30 1
	  		SETEVENT 85 2 ALWAYS
  			CONTEVENT 85
      			RANDOM DUMMY1 1 4 0
      			IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
        			ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "Tell me mortal, am I the mightiest of dragons?"
      			ENDIF
      			IFVAR DUMMY1 = 2
        			ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "Tell me mortal, am I not the wisest upon Andor?"
      			ENDIF
      			IFVAR DUMMY1 = 3
        			ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "Tell me mortal, do I have the greatest cache of treasure upon Andor?"
      			ENDIF
  			IFVAR DUMMY1 = 4
  				ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "Tell me mortal, am I the greatest wielder of magic in all of time?"
      			ENDIF
    		ENDIF
  	ENDIF
  	IFVAR INTNUM79 = 111
    		ECHO ALL Ming-K'tuk roars, "I recognize you now, %N. You have served me in the past and earned a reward. No tribute shall you need... you may pass."
  	ENDIF
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 1811
REGION 2
NAME Deep Realms, Lair of Ming-K'Tuk
FIXED_LIGHT
DEEPCAVE
RELOGIN 1810
CHANNEL 82
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This cavern is enormous. The heavy elkyri door to the west is but a tiny
portion of this chamber. Before you is the great wyrm, Ming-K'Tuk. Behind him,
though a massive archway, lay breathtaking mounds of gold and silver intermixed
with thousands of glittering gems. Supremely crafted weapons, silk tapestries,
masterful statues and suits of armor lay strewn about as if some child had
forgotten to pick up their toys. These amazing examples of wealth are
surpassed only by the chests and trunks laying half-buried in the hoard,
heaping with magnificent jewelry and other items that your mind can only
begin to fathom. A passageway continues to the east.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 73 VAL2=1812
ITEM 1 60 ADJ1=189
ITEM 4 65 ADJ1=156 ADJ2=109 VAL1=9999 VAL2=1810 LOCKED CLOSED
;
IFENTRY
	IFVAR MAKEDRAGON = 0
		IFVAR PVAL90 = 0
			GENMON 294
			EQUAL MAKEDRAGON 1
		ELSE
			ROOMCOPY 1813
			NEWITEM 1 232 ADJ1=99
		ENDIF
	ELSE
		IFVAR PVAL90 = 0
      			SETEVENT 84 2 ALWAYS
			CONTEVENT 84
      			ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "Mortals!  What tribute hath thou for me?"
    		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
;
IFVAR PVAL90 = 0
	IFVAR INTNUM30 = 1
		IFVAR FLAG1 = 1
			IFSAY passage
				EQUAL DJUSTTAIL 1
				EQUAL DRAGONTAIL 1
				ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk moves his tail, allowing entry to the eastern passage.
				AFFECT 1812
				ECHO ALL You see Ming-K'Tuk move his tail, allowing entry to the western passage.
			ENDIF
			IFSAY wisdom
				ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "Discourse with mortals does not interest me today, but I will let you pass beyond my chamber if you have an offering that interests me."
				EQUAL FLAG1 2
			ENDIF
		ELSE
			IFVAR FLAG1 = 2
				IFSAY Ming-K'Tuk?
					ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "That be I, mightiest of dragonkind!"
				ENDIF
			ELSE
				IFSAY aye
					ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk appears to be satisfied with your flattery.
					ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "Now that thou hath interrupted my rest, hath thou cometh seeking my wisdom or simply passage?"
					EQUAL FLAG1 1
				ENDIF
				IFSAY yes
					ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk appears to be satisfied with your flattery.
					ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk roars, "Now that thou hath interrupted my rest, hath thou cometh seeking my wisdom or simply passage?"
					EQUAL FLAG1 1
				ENDIF				
				IFSAY nay
					ECHO ALL Ming-K'Tuk didn't seem to hear what you said.
				ENDIF
			ENDIF
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
