	CLEARVERB
	IFVAR RAC = 5
		ECHO PLAYER      Oh children of the deep,%c     You are the chosen that I keep.%c     For you are loyal and in it shall find%c     the power and wisdom%c     that others shall be denied.
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER You can not read murg.
	ENDIF
